    <string-array
        name="version_descriptions_list">
        <item>- Manual export to Dropbox.
            \n- “What\'s new” dialog.
            \n- Initial loading screen.
            \n- “Simple repeat” task repeat mode now in quick access repeat dialog.
            \n- Partial data reset possibility(will not delete tasks/skills).
            \n- Fixed desktop widget. Press on widget now opens details for selected task.
            \n- Fixed incorrect XP value displaying during hero level up.
            \n- Fixed some crashes related to decreasing skills.</item>
        <item>- Added floating action buttons.
            \n- Redesigned Settings and other lists in application.
            \n- Separate notification will be shown for each task.
            \n- Added sound signal to notifications.
            \n- What\'s new dialog can be displayed via Settings > About.
            \n- Fixed crashes on navigation between screens.
            \n- Fixed some localization strings.</item>
        <item>- Added skills chart.
            \n- Some networking improvements.
            \n- Fixed bug with reappearing characteristics.
            \n- Fixed few rarely reproduced crashes.</item>
        <item>- Moved to new Dropbox API v.2.
            \n- Reduced Dropbox notification visibility time.
            \n- Optional, only todays tasks in To Do tab (can be turned on/off via Settings).
            \n- Optional, show dailies in Done tab with last execution date (can be turned on/off via Settings).
            \n- Skip feature for tasks with specified date. When skip button pressed – date will be changed to nearest one by specified in task rule.
</item>
        <item>-	Possibility to set custom avatar from file system.
            \n-	Possibility to set new avatar right from camera.
            \n-	Added sounds on level up and skill up (can be switched on/off in settings).
</item>
    </string-array>

